name: InSomnia - Tactical Cooperative RPG (Canceled)
blurb: InSomnia - a tactical Cooperative RPG with unique game mechanics in a dark retro-futuristic dieselpunk setting

rewards.reward: \u2018I Would Like To Thank\u2026\u2019\r\nThank you for your pledge! We couldn\u2019t do this without you. Every backer at this level will receive an exclusive downloadable content pack with all the gorgeous InSomnia imagery including - wallpapers, concept art, screenshots. You are also \r\ninvited on to our forums so that you can take part in the discussions with the development team on the direction of the game going forward.

'The Music Aficionado'\r\nThe \u2018Thank-You!\u2019 reward plus Kickstarter backer Forum Badge and a digital download copy of the original InSomnia soundtrack. You are also invited on to our forums so that you can take part in the discussions with the development team on the direction of the game going forward.
"I just want this Game" - You will receive the digital copy of the game, as well as the gratitude from InSomnia team!
\u2018The VIP Area!\u2019\r\nFor the first 2000 backers only! A digital copy of the game, all previous rewards AND one in game special item(The item will not affect the game's balance).

'The Historian'\r\nAll previous rewards plus: Closed Beta access for May 2014 AND Prologue Chapter (DLC KS backers only); several single-player and co-op missions and quests set in the past that introduces the story of InSomnia.

\u2018The Book Worm!\u2019\r\nAll previous rewards plus: a digital copy of the InSomnia Art Book featuring the stunning character and environment concept artwork of famed British fantasy artist Adrian Smith and other talented artists. And there\u2019s more! A Kickstarter exclusive In-Game avatar only available to backers!

'The Art Critic'\r\nAll previous rewards plus: High quality printed InSomnia poster designed by famed British fantasy artist Adrian Smith and signed by the development team, as well as a boxed copy of the game.

\u2018Look At Me!\u2019\r\nAll previous rewards plus: Custom In-Game Sign, exclusively developed by one of our game artists that you will be able to use on forums as well as in-game on shields and armor to make your character even more distinctive. Plus, name in the credits of the game.

\u2018Weapon Unlock!\u2019\r\nAll previous rewards plus: Signed Collectors boxed copy of the game AND a unique in-game weapon designed by you and implemented by our 2d and 3d artists! An incredible opportunity to own a specially designed weapon that no-one else in the game will be able to own!(The item will not affect the game's balance).

"The Descendent of the Great Republic!"\r\nAll previous rewards + a unique custom avatar and in-game head skin based on your suggestions. You\u2019ll also receive a special character biography and social abilities that will allow for additional gameplay without affecting the game balance.
"Outfit Pack Unlock"\r\nAll previous rewards + custom faction outfit pack designed by you. These items will not affect the game balance but will give your faction a distinctive look.

"Join the Epic Saga!"\r\nAll previous rewards + inclusion of your character\u2019s biography in the main storyline associated with one of three playable factions. You will also receive special abilities along with a customized full outfit pack and domiciles. You will be the key character in events involving the entire world affecting a large number of players. Your decisions will have a huge influence on the storyline!
